data.description: Make yourself at home in this charming 2-bed, 2-bath twin home in the Adult Community of Sun City! Offering brick accents, a lush lawn, carport parking, & a delightful back patio. Discover a sizable living/dining room adorned with soothing paint, wood-style flooring, chic light fixtures, & a mirrored wall accent elevating the space. The family room has French doors to the back, making entertaining a bliss. The kitchen provides new appliances, quartz counters, mosaic tile backsplash, plantation shutters, & a service window. Plenty of white cabinetry & a handy pantry ensures ample storage space. Carpeted main bedroom features a vanity area, a dedicated bathroom, & a walk-in closet. Enjoy afternoon relaxation on the private patio! The roof, sewer, and A/C were all recently updated!
